sec.p:
Many studies have used methanol for the extraction of cyanotoxins (
  Codd, 2000; 
  Fyumagwa et al., 2013; 
  Kim et al., 2009; 
  Mbukwa et al., 2012; 
  Merel et al., 2013; 
  Metcalf and Codd, 2014). The approach was challenged by a recent study (
  Visser et al., 2016) which question the validity of the previous findings. This is still debatable.
